\n<div class=\"s3\"><strong><span class=\"s2\">1. Tape-ins</span></strong></div>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-71\" src=\"https://hairlife.style/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/D0910EA7-E1FC-46A2-A529-02B251A7A4FB-300x288.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"288\" />\n\nSome people desire long and thick hair; it is the main reason they are committed to finding products that can help them retain length and maintain healthy hair. Tape-ins are a quick and easy way to add thickness and length to your hair. There are various Tape-in options with different textures, colours, and lengths. Tape-ins give instant transformation taking 20 to 60 minutes to install. They are comfortable and can be installed on natural or chemically treated hair.\n\nTape-ins are designed to be weightless, and with different textures and colours, they easily blend into your hair. As a result, you can quickly install and uninstall tape-ins to create a variety of hairstyles, from sleek ponytails to loose curls. Some tape-ins are reusable, so you can use them multiple times to get your desired hairstyle. If you are worried about maintenance, tape-ins are low-maintenance and waterproof, so that you can enjoy a day in the pool without concerns about your tape-ins slipping.\n\nWhile installing tape-ins is quick and easy, it is recommended to get the services of a licensed cosmetologist for safer installation and removal of your tape-ins. This will ensure that your hair is not damaged during the installation and removal process.\n<div class=\"s3\"><b>2. <span class=\"s2\">Boho</span><span class=\"s2\"> kn</span></b><b><span class=\"s2\">otless</span></b></div>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-73\" src=\"https://hairlife.style/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/D0FA2011-9A55-4C27-BDDA-BC387D1EB2DC-245x300.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"245\" height=\"300\" />\n\nBraids have been popular for a long time, but over the last couple of months, boho knotless braids have become very popular because they level-up traditional box braids. These braids do not have a knot at the root where the extension is added, so they are lightweight, put less tension on the scalp, and have a more natural and seamless appearance.\n\nWhile they may take a while to install, depending on the thickness and length of the braids, they are quite easy to maintain and can easily be worn out in all kinds of weather. For best results and to ensure that you have neat braids for longer, it is recommended to use human hair for the curly bits. Synthetic hair tends to get tangled creating a matted, unsightly mess.\n\nOnce you get boho knotless braids, you need to focus on moisturizing your hair and keeping it clean, and when you take them out, you will notice significant growth and length retention. In addition, they are painless and gentle on your edges!\n\nBoho knotless braids offer a variety of hairstyles too. You can let them down with a simple part in the middle, hold them up in a bun, play around with different colours, or get them in a bob style. This hairstyle is simple and versatile.\n<div class=\"s3\"><span class=\"s2\"><b>3. Pin-up</b></span></div>\n<div><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-74\" src=\"https://hairlife.style/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/C66ED850-CE4E-4199-A883-0868FC16CD67-248x300.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"248\" height=\"300\" /></div>\nPin-up hairstyles are characterized by volume, instantly bringing a vintage vibe that is perfect for the modern girl. The most popular pin-up hairstyle is the pin-up ponytail, but the pin-up bun with bangs is quite common too. This hairstyle is easy and can be done on any hair texture. Most recognizably, pin-up hairstyles can be done on wigs or natural hair, and all you need is some glued hair spray, bobby pins, and hair ties to hold your pin-up updo in place.\n\nThis hairstyle is quite versatile. You can opt for a side swoop,middle part bangs, or no bangs and add accessories to add personality to the hairstyle. Most people love to add the fishtail braid to spice up their updo. The simplicity in styling and appearance of the pin-up makes it one of the go-to hairstyles for weddings and prom.\n\nThere are numerous quick and easy hairstyles to choose from, but these three guarantee comfort and style without too much effort in the styling process. Fortunately, getting a great hairstyle doesn’t have to be hard or time-consuming.","Top 3 Hairstyles and Why We Love Them","","publish","open","open","","67-2","","","2023-01-04 16:56:22","2023-01-04 16:56:22","","0","https://hairlife.style/blog/?p=67","0","post","","0"),
